\title{bRunching: Bunching Correction Estimators for Censored Treatments}
\description{
Implements the Caetano, Caetano, and Nielsen (CCN) bunching correction estimator for regression models with a treatment variable censored at zero. When many observations bunch at zero, naive OLS is biased. This package estimates the censored expectation under uniform, Tobit, or symmetry assumptions and includes it as a correction term. Supports homogeneous and heterogeneous treatment effects, heterogeneous correction terms, and discontinuity plots at the bunching point.
